{"tid":2064970,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"《熱戀》","createTime":"2020-06-15T07:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T11:45:37.000Z","uid":194824,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f27897fc7cc9cf5359ce4f7f80899920dafa109","tid":2064970,"uid":194824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"「喂，我地要一生一世呀。」<br />\n「唔好離開我喎。」<br />\n「我愛你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n千言萬語，甜言蜜語，萬千承諾隨之而誕生。<br />\n望住對方嘅眼神，包含住自己個面貌，甜絲絲，好難忘，係佢喇，佢就係我鍾意嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱戀就好似一舊碩大多汁嘅果實，初初男女咬落去都會覺得新鮮無比，甜而不膩，好想一直咬落去，直至榨乾榨淨。<br />\n<br />\n你一啖我一啖，拖住手仔行海濱，睇大家都鍾意嘅電影，你錫下我我錫下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好唔捨得咁要各自番屋企，感嘆時間唔夠多，好想好想同你永永遠遠係埋一齊做大家想做嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴絲隨便分享下熱戀時果種好開心好難忘嘅回憶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d032bc11ee6f74af8e105403b8f82298bb797793","tid":2064970,"uid":180040,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:56:10.000Z","msg":"初吻嘅時候佢俾兩粒糖我揀 <br />\n然後佢食住黎錫我 <br />\n要我永遠記得呢隻味<br />\n佢最後雖然同我行唔到去最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我永遠都記得我初戀係咩味"},{"pid":"9395d1b46a0c2d8809ac63ff04ff1b28a2af4477","tid":2064970,"uid":194824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"有冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n6.15 義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/cat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02d6e0008f911201b54e2499bbaab1593ca0161","tid":2064970,"uid":152040,"like":0,"dis